svg.text: Push all holding mechanisms with LEDs, clamps and the acrylic sheets attached from behind into​the sparepartscontainer.

text.style: fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 50px; white-space: pre;

svg.text: Put in every indent on the back of the holding mechanisms a 10mm neodym magnet to secure​them more in place.​

text.style: fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 50px; white-space: pre;

svg.text: After this you can hook up all LEDs together and connect them to the ESP32 via the jumper cables.
